message: Hello Bob, I'm excited to present our premium product which has been meticulously designed and crafted with excellence in mind. This product is not just an item; it's a testament to quality and innovation. Given its unique features and unparalleled craftsmanship, I believe its value exceeds $8000. Considering its exceptional nature, I am offering it to you for $12000. This is a special opportunity to own something truly remarkable. Please let me know if you're interested in discussing this further.
